data.description: Welcome to this charming home in the heart of Coldspring! Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this property offers a cozy and inviting atmosphere that is sure to make you feel right at home. The interior has been freshly painted in cool colors and new flooring has been installed throughout. The open concept living area features a wood burning fireplace and the updated kitchen boasts butcher block counter tops, oversized farmhouse sink, ample counter space and a separate dining area where you can enjoy meals with loved ones. Outside you will find a covered patio, fenced yard and a workshop offering a great space for DIY projects or storage. Located just a few blocks off the Coldspring Courthouse Square you'll have easy access to local amenities, shops and restaurants. For those who enjoy outdoor activities, Lake Livingston is just a short drive away for fishing, boating and water-based adventures.
